column1: Narthseg was an Elf of Artanor.
Narthseg belonged to the people of Artanor
column2: but later betrayed both Artanor and Thingol his king by revealing crucial information to Naugladur lord of Nogrod which resulted in Tinwelints death and the sack of Artanor.
